{"tid":601294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"表情恐懼症屬於社交恐懼症的一種表現","createTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T11:48:19.000Z","uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d768e3bf125e80ee4e170fb6ae90ce3b66bf34","tid":601294,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"表情恐懼症屬於社交恐懼症的一種表現，因為性格的內心或過於敏感導致的心理和行為障礙。需進行針對性的心理諮詢和治療進行調整。<br />\n<br />\n（1）有的人擔心自己的面部表情不自然；<br />\n（2）有的人擔心自己的不自然的表情影響到別人；<br />\n（3）有的人總是關注自己的表情不知道使用什麼樣的表情；<br />\n（4）不是擔心自己的臉部表情、而是認為確實是臉部表情損害了人際關係 確實是表情不好。與心理患者接觸的人都怕他。很自責和內疚。<br />\n（5）患者總擔心自己的面部表情會引起別人的反感，或被人看不起，對此慌恐不安。表情恐懼多與眼神有關。患者認為自己眼神令其他人生畏，或認為自己的眼神毫無光彩等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗住日日戴口罩出街，因為中左9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b04dd9a9b946932bb4fb50fc9a4af56a8381a00","tid":601294,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"中咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e93c4e2bb167436455916c934bbf921f86c515b","tid":601294,"uid":10788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"口罩好有安全感 唔洗諗用咩表情對住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fca9fa0492dc3beaf7c61ad8c2d226be1a9c507","tid":601294,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"其實<br />\n<br />\n根本冇人留意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dffe22656cef5350318c8735562d8fc37ece639","tid":601294,"uid":78425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"靚仔咪自然囉 唔靚仔緊係唔自然啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88806bfc078f3ae6be2a09a5df003cc9e1f32ff6","tid":601294,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"搭地鐵要企角落"},{"pid":"e73bcfd2072a193e115d4e4f8845427c75dbc7ec","tid":601294,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"時事台?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59da5d720ef43ee0c757ca727cc24e9e46ffde53","tid":601294,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f7004c0c4e722bf04555f914084802c073df6c","tid":601294,"uid":82749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚仔咪自然囉 唔靚仔緊係唔自然啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚仔先會介意<br />\n唔靚仔咩表情都係柒，介意黎做乜"}]}